    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>278264</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_170_040_001</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>これであの弱虫も、
勝手に外へ出るなどの
わがままはしなくなる</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That coward is too wrapped up in his own personal delirium 
to face the outside world and help you. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>279220</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_170_040_002</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Dio&gt;は
弱虫なんかじゃない！
きっと……！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That's not true! &lt;Dio&gt; isn't a coward! He...! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>279360</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_170_040_003</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>知らなくてもいいことを知り、
歪むくらいなら
何も知らない方が幸せだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Know nothing and shut your eyes to the world. He's happy 
with being ignorant. It's a simple way to live by. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>279360</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_170_040_004</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>おまえとて、外の世界に
出るのは不安だったのだろう</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You're trying to embrace this world. But in the end all 
that's inside of you is insecurity. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>279612</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_170_040_005</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……たしかに、すごく不安だけど
それを乗り越えるのが
楽しいっていうか……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...It's true I'm very scared and sometimes I'm lost. But 
overcoming all of that is what made this journey worth it...! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>280844</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_170_040_006</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……よくわからないけど、
だからこそ、そこに新しいもの
を見つけられる気がして</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...I can't easily put it into words, but there are many 
things I want to see. Everything new in this world teaches us and 
makes us stronger... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>282412</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_170_040_007</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>違う、かな？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That's what I...think...? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>282888</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_170_040_008</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……うん、そう、だと思う</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yes...I'm sure. That's my belief. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>284124</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_170_040_009</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……ふん</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Mph. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>284812</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_170_040_010</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>きゃあっ！！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Aaaah! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>286300</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_170_040_011</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>クルール！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Kururu! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>286440</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_170_040_012</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Mel&gt;……！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Mel&gt;, are you okay!? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>286736</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_170_040_013</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>家でおとなしくしていれば、
こんな恐ろしい目に
遭わなくても済むものを</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You wouldn't have to suffer this much if should have 
obediently stayed inside your house. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>287368</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_170_040_014</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>それ以上、&lt;Mel&gt;に近づくな！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Stay away from &lt;Mel&gt;! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>289152</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_170_040_015</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Mel&gt;！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Mel&gt;! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>14</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>290904</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_170_040_016</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>…………</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>15</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>291464</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_170_040_017</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Mel&gt;を傷つけたりしたら、
ひどいぞ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I won't forgive anyone who hurts &lt;Mel&gt;! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>16</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>291660</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_170_040_018</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Dio&gt;……！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Dio&gt;! You came...! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>17</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>291800</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_170_040_019</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>やるか……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Fine. Be that way... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>18</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
